#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.Series.to_json.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.Series.to\\_json"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_json.to_json:1 of
msgid "Convert the object to a JSON string."
msgstr "将对象转换为 JSON 字符串。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_json.to_json:3 of
msgid ""
"Note NaN's and None will be converted to null and datetime objects will "
"be converted to UNIX timestamps."
msgstr "注意 NaN 和 None 将被转换为 null，日期时间对象将被转换为 UNIX 时间戳。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_json.to_json of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_json.to_json:6 of
msgid ""
"String, path object (implementing os.PathLike[str]), or file-like object "
"implementing a write() function. If None, the result is returned as a "
"string."
msgstr ""
"字符串、路径对象（实现 os.PathLike[str]）或实现 write() 函数的类文件对象"
"。如果为 None，则结果以字符串形式返回。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_json.to_json:10 of
msgid ""
"Indication of expected JSON string format.  * Series:      - default is "
"'index'     - allowed values are: {'split', 'records', 'index', 'table'}."
"  * DataFrame:      - default is 'columns'     - allowed values are: "
"{'split', 'records', 'index', 'columns',       'values', 'table'}.  * The"
" format of the JSON string:      - 'split' : dict like {'index' -> "
"[index], 'columns' -> [columns],       'data' -> [values]}     - "
"'records' : list like [{column -> value}, ... , {column -> value}]     - "
"'index' : dict like {index -> {column -> value}}     - 'columns' : dict "
"like {column -> {index -> value}}     - 'values' : just the values array"
"     - 'table' : dict like {'schema': {schema}, 'data': {data}}      "
"Describing the data, where data component is like ``orient='records'``."
msgstr ""
"指示期望的 JSON 字符串格式。  * Series:      - 默认是 'index'     - 允许"
"的值为：{'split', 'records', 'index', 'table'}。  * DataFrame:      - "
"默认是 'columns'     - 允许的值为：{'split', 'records', 'index', 'columns"
"',       'values', 'table'}。  * JSON 字符串的格式:      - 'split' : 类似"
" {'index' -> [index], 'columns' -> [columns],       'data' -> [values]} "
"的字典     - 'records' : 类似 [{column -> value}, ... , {column -> value}"
"] 的列表     - 'index' : 类似 {index -> {column -> value}} 的字典     - '"
"columns' : 类似 {column -> {index -> value}} 的字典     - 'values' : 仅值"
"数组     - 'table' : 类似 {'schema': {schema}, 'data': {data}} 的字典    "
"  描述数据，其中 data 部分类似 ``orient='records'``。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_json.to_json:10 of
msgid "Indication of expected JSON string format."
msgstr "指示期望的 JSON 字符串格式。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_json.to_json:12 of
msgid "Series:"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_json.to_json:14 of
msgid "default is 'index'"
msgstr "默认为 'index'"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_json.to_json:15 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid "allowed values are: {'split', 'records', 'index', 'table'}."
msgstr "允许的值为：{'split', 'records', 'index', 'table'}。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_json.to_json:17 of
msgid "DataFrame:"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_json.to_json:19 of
msgid "default is 'columns'"
msgstr "默认为 'columns'"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_json.to_json:20 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"allowed values are: {'split', 'records', 'index', 'columns', 'values', "
"'table'}."
msgstr "允许的值为：{'split', 'records', 'index', 'columns', 'values', 'table'}。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_json.to_json:23 of
msgid "The format of the JSON string:"
msgstr "JSON 字符串的格式："

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_json.to_json:25 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"'split' : dict like {'index' -> [index], 'columns' -> [columns], 'data' "
"-> [values]}"
msgstr ""
"'split' : 类似 {'index' -> [index], 'columns' -> [columns], 'data' -> ["
"values]} 的字典"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_json.to_json:27 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid "'records' : list like [{column -> value}, ... , {column -> value}]"
msgstr "'records' : 类似 [{column -> value}, ... , {column -> value}] 的列表"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_json.to_json:28 of
msgid "'index' : dict like {index -> {column -> value}}"
msgstr "'index' : 类似 {index -> {column -> value}} 的字典"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_json.to_json:29 of
msgid "'columns' : dict like {column -> {index -> value}}"
msgstr "'columns' : 类似 {column -> {index -> value}} 的字典"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_json.to_json:30 of
msgid "'values' : just the values array"
msgstr "'values' : 仅值数组"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_json.to_json:31 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid "'table' : dict like {'schema': {schema}, 'data': {data}}"
msgstr "'table' : 类似 {'schema': {schema}, 'data': {data}} 的字典"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_json.to_json:33 of
msgid "Describing the data, where data component is like ``orient='records'``."
msgstr "描述数据，其中 data 部分类似 ``orient='records'``。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_json.to_json:35 of
msgid ""
"Type of date conversion. 'epoch' = epoch milliseconds, 'iso' = ISO8601. "
"The default depends on the `orient`. For ``orient='table'``, the default "
"is 'iso'. For all other orients, the default is 'epoch'."
msgstr ""
"日期转换类型。'epoch' = 纪元毫秒，'iso' = ISO8601。默认值取决于 `orient`"
"。对于 ``orient='table'``，默认值是 'iso'。对于所有其他 orient，默认值是 "
"'epoch'。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_json.to_json:40 of
msgid "The number of decimal places to use when encoding floating point numbers."
msgstr "编码浮点数时使用的小数位数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_json.to_json:43 of
msgid "Force encoded string to be ASCII."
msgstr "强制编码后的字符串为 ASCII 格式。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_json.to_json:45 of
msgid ""
"The time unit to encode to, governs timestamp and ISO8601 precision.  One"
" of 's', 'ms', 'us', 'ns' for second, millisecond, microsecond, and "
"nanosecond respectively."
msgstr ""
"编码的时间单位，控制时间戳和 ISO8601 精度。可选值为 's', 'ms', 'us', 'ns'"
"，分别表示秒、毫秒、微秒和纳秒。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_json.to_json:49 of
msgid ""
"Handler to call if object cannot otherwise be converted to a suitable "
"format for JSON. Should receive a single argument which is the object to "
"convert and return a serializable object."
msgstr ""
"如果对象无法转换为适合 JSON 的格式时调用的处理程序。应接收一个参数，即要"
"转换的对象，并返回一个可序列化的对象。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_json.to_json:53 of
msgid ""
"If 'orient' is 'records' write out line-delimited json format. Will throw"
" ValueError if incorrect 'orient' is used."
msgstr ""
"如果 'orient' 是 'records'，则写出行分隔的 JSON 格式。如果使用了不正确的 "
"'orient'，将抛出 ValueError。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_json.to_json:56 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"For on-the-fly compression of the output data. If str, represents "
"compression mode. If dict, value at 'method' is the compression mode. "
"Compression mode may be any of the following possible values: {'infer', "
"'gzip', 'bz2', 'zip', 'xz', None}. If compression mode is 'infer' and "
"`path_or_buf` is path-like, then detect compression mode from the "
"following extensions: '.gz', '.bz2', '.zip' or '.xz'. (otherwise no "
"compression). If dict given and mode is one of {'zip', 'xz'}, other "
"entries passed as additional compression options."
msgstr ""
"用于输出数据的即时压缩。如果是字符串，则表示压缩模式。如果是字典，则 '"
"method' 处的值为压缩模式。压缩模式可以是以下可能值中的任意一个：{'infer',"
" 'gzip', 'bz2', 'zip', 'xz', None}。如果压缩模式是 'infer' 且 `path_or_"
"buf` 是路径类型，则从以下扩展名中检测压缩模式：'.gz', '.bz2', '.zip' 或 '"
".xz'。（否则不压缩）。如果给出的是字典且模式是 {'zip', 'xz'} 之一，则其他"
"条目作为附加压缩选项传递。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_json.to_json:66 of
msgid ""
"Whether to include the index values in the JSON string. Not including the"
" index (``index=False``) is only supported when orient is 'split' or "
"'table'."
msgstr ""
"是否在 JSON 字符串中包含索引值。不包含索引（``index=False``）仅在 orient "
"为 'split' 或 'table' 时支持。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_json.to_json:70 of
msgid "Length of whitespace used to indent each record."
msgstr "用于缩进每条记录的空白字符长度。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_json.to_json:72 of
msgid ""
"Column names by which to partition the dataset. Columns are partitioned "
"in the order they are given."
msgstr "用于对数据集进行分区的列名。列按照给定的顺序进行分区。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_json.to_json:78 of
msgid ":py:obj:`read_json`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_json.to_json:79 of
msgid "Convert a JSON string to pandas object."
msgstr "将 JSON 字符串转换为 pandas 对象。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_json.to_json:82 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_json.to_json:83 of
msgid ""
"The behavior of ``indent=0`` varies from the stdlib, which does not "
"indent the output but does insert newlines. Currently, ``indent=0`` and "
"the default ``indent=None`` are equivalent in pandas, though this may "
"change in a future release."
msgstr ""
"``indent=0`` 的行为与标准库不同，标准库不会缩进输出但会插入换行符。目前在"
" pandas 中，``indent=0`` 与默认值 ``indent=None`` 等效，尽管这在未来版本"
"中可能会改变。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_json.to_json:88 of
msgid ""
"``orient='table'`` contains a 'pandas_version' field under 'schema'. This"
" stores the version of `pandas` used in the latest revision of the "
"schema."
msgstr ""
"``orient='table'`` 在 'schema' 下包含一个 'pandas_version' 字段。这存储了"
"在 schema 最新修订版中使用的 `pandas` 版本。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_json.to_json:93 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""
